      "content": "but it doesnt feel like a gift. it feels like a burden. they keep seeing me struggle and cry and fail, and it’s just... it's toxic for them. if i stayed, i'm just teaching them how to be miserable. wouldn't it be more selfless to just get out of the way so they can actually have a chance at a normal, happy life?",
